obimetinib, Capmatinib, Ibrutinib, Afatinib, Tivozanib, More', 'Dextromethorphan, Dalfampridine, Sodium oxybate, Riluzole, Inotersen, Pitolisant, Amifampridine, Tafamidis', 1767369485);
